{"tid":662704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"google喺《Nature》發表論文 示範如何喺電子健康紀錄中「尋寶」","createTime":"2018-05-12T15:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T00:46:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"36f3261811d3d2f92182672f6c1ba3da6bf9fff1","tid":662704,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"深度學習演算法（Deep learning）在最近幾年突飛猛進，早已成為我們生活無聲無息的一部份。無論是 Google Translate、Snapchat 的智能面部裝飾、抑或是辨認人面的監控鏡頭，一切都建基於深度學習。<br />\n<br />\n今天 Everest 想介紹日常少見的應用場景：公共醫療。Google 最近在《Nature》期刊發表了《Scalable and accurate deep learning with electronic health record》一文，展示了深度學習為醫療系統開源節流、提高效率的潛力。簡單而言，Google 利用十九萬名（美國）病人的病歷訓練深度學習模型，讓電腦尋找病歷中的規律，然後利用剩餘兩萬人的病歷證明模型可靠；例如，可以估算病人是否需要多次入院。<br />\n<br />\n希望聽過簡報後，你也會明白這篇論文的意義。深度學習的技術細節，反而不太重要。下回再分享！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w5BOM4gcKVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw5BOM4gcKVM&d=GbHFx9fPnIZYCTYeHDbp7V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=79d8c204\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w5BOM4gcKVM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@everestphyl/在電子健康紀錄中-尋寶-b54becfef8c6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40everestphyl%2F%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E4%B8%AD-%E5%B0%8B%E5%AF%B6-b54becfef8c6&d=GbHFx9fPnIZYCTYeHDbp7V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=28651eba\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@everestphyl/在電子健康紀錄中-尋寶-b54becfef8c6</a>"},{"pid":"24e907980dee15f91a065a28be53fb65a26f9ee2","tid":662704,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"論文link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41746-018-0029-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41746-018-0029-1&d=GbHFx9fPnIZYCTYeHDbp7V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b0bd575b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41746-018-0029-1</a>"},{"pid":"b62f374febcb3aec6cdd2c73f7be5462ef7b41a6","tid":